Articles.Content:
I'm playing 1.8.1 modded, I wanted to set a new orbit for a probe I launched days before but I could not add manouvers, I tryied to do so with other older vessels and it was the same. I then launched a new probe into orbit on which I could set manouvers, I warped fast some days in the track station and returned to it to see If I still could but I didn't. My track station is level 3 and every vessel I tryied this on was connected to KSC.
